","date":"2026-05-22T09:01:10Z"},"message":"fix(mime): specify charset parameter per MIME type instead of mechanical detection (#4912)\n\nPer #4510:\n\n- Inline `; charset=utf-8` in `_baseMimes` for all text/* entries plus\n  `image/svg+xml`, `application/xhtml+xml`, and `application/xml`,\n  which are XML-based formats that benefit from an explicit charset.\n- Drop the `if (mimeType.startsWith(\"text\"))` block in `getMimeType`;\n  the charset now lives in the data, not in the lookup logic. Output\n  for text types is unchanged (still \"text/<sub>; charset=utf-8\").\n- Update `getExtension` to compare the base type (the part before the\n  first `;`), so callers can pass either a raw type (\"text/html\") or\n  one with parameters (\"text/html; charset=utf-8\") and still get the\n  correct extension back.\n\nTests: 5 mime.test.ts cases pass (3 existing + 2 new) covering the new\ncharset values for svg/xhtml/xml/ics/mjs/css/csv and getExtension with\nparameters.\n\nCloses #4510","tree":{"sha":"1cc19390cef8813c784820154caddc6b3e084547","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/honojs/hono/git/trees/1cc19390cef8813c784820154caddc6b3e084547"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/honojs/hono/git/commits/a192df0844724aeaf5cbc6f1ea2f8425d3f8a86a","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJqEBtWCRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAAaVUQAFENgucypWpDSIammFQR5Dwa\n2OuaRDFz3FTgDvBkfojK6t9BNqibNtWc3o8R6v4l2E3gij9PkM8Kqv2ViKQg7D6d\n9jOtC6rBLxZ7cLt8iHCNysXWweVdSK34bq2q0U+vbkOSriI9znM6qYu2v8mwaqMh\n03byHA4kFEuiIpJOEH2zLUgt/XsB7mDM8jmQKA+lrLV+pE4mRt6sIKEL9JT67tqO\ngDwAtBDTrS6G9h2YFDxx2vzc3KCY/XQQDJlVLdDSNuP/6kMAzweqJKAbVEI2jqjk\nEkmjR14x9/kFm+YQRq0gWwJ1xvsMldr4RQTV/eAW+TixvDeUapBGzlCVJmloYXg4\neFyxIrJgLGWd6xlx20tC08r4WZdMqed17E+l8Rrtp89jtR42CzV9pO4/M882iXjr\nITp0RzhsZRRovg1lYYSddUdsgE6+ugC4GqTpSyxqk7qrjYCuEjbhoM4m7S+2XRSc\nfXicpv2zOO65OT4rSFQ84MOuiRx+RRxAEpaxXNBBOc7tpnyFnC/FTekfV/ux8I2m\npkxBBLSp77/cJwZ3RAWRy/7t0j+IcVGB6AOeQtfiL